column5: Just wondering. Heading up in a couple of weeks. Looks like it has rained a little.
That rain brought the lake up..  TWO inches! I'll have another report by weeks end.
Hey 10point.....what dates are you going to be up there???...I'm heading up in a couple of weeks to.
We arrive on the 27th. Staying at Tamar.
Won't be up until the following week..
leaving Saturday the 19th for a week in Diamond Lake, Will let you know when I get back
six of of us going to diamond lake with two rookies this year me fang benny and rob and two rookies are they in for a surprise when they get there
Are you guys staying at Rick's place?

I wish I could bring some water with me. We had 3 inches of rain last night and expect another inch in the next 24 hours. It rains like everyday here now and lost of roads are closed due to flooding. At least we haven't had to water the flowers this year.
